csc143.sudoku

Interface CoordinateTransform


  • public interface CoordinateTransform
    This interface supports the transform of between row/column and region/ordinal coordinates for a cell in SudokuBoard. Needless to say, these transforms depend on the current value of rows and columns in the underlying SudokuBase.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      csc143.sudoku.RegOrd toRegOrg(csc143.sudoku.RowCol coord)
      Transform the row/column coordinates for a cell into region/ordinal coordinates.
      csc143.sudoku.RowCol toRowCol(csc143.sudoku.RegOrd coord)
      Transform the region/ordinal coordinates for a cell into row/column coordinates.
